  "title": "Senior / Project Engineer (BMS / ELV / M&E)",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Well established Company</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Basic $3700 - $ 5500 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Working location: West (Singapore) </strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Working hours: 8:30am – 5:30pm</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>5 days’ work week</strong><br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong><br /></p><ul><li><p><strong>Involve in conceptual and details design of Mechanical / Electrical / BMS engineering works</strong></p></li><li><p>Assist Manager in Project Planning, Budget Cost Control and execution of Project</p></li><li><p><strong>Coordinate with Main Con and other contractors for BMS installation work</strong></p></li><li><p>Supervise a group of subcontractors and ensure that works are executed within and acceptable standard of workmanship</p></li><li><p><strong>Prepare site progress report and necessary project documentation that may include method statement</strong></p></li><li><p>Ensure timely handover (delivery) of project while maintaining high quality standard of optimum cost (cost effectiveness)</p></li><li><p><strong>Ensure that the relevant installation drawings are accessible at the point of use</strong></p></li><li><p>Review the nature of non-conformities detected in product / work and determine the disposition of the non-conformities</p></li><li><p><strong>Resolve technical issues relating to installation, commissioning and testing</strong></p></li><li><p>Responsibility for the successful completion of the projects and meet customers satisfaction<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br /></p><ul><li><p>Diploma in <strong>Electrical and Electronics or Mechanical Engineering </strong>or equivalent</p></li><li><p>Candidate with lesser experience are welcome to apply – Training will be provided<br /></p><p></p></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the resume<br /></p><ul><li><p>Work experiences and job responsibilities</p></li><li><p>Current and Expected salary</p></li><li><p>Reason for leaving</p></li><li><p>Date of availability</p></li><li><p>Education background<br /></p><p></p></li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.<br /></p><p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
